To setup the project

1. Clone the repo
2. Inspect and run setup.sh to create the .rpmmacros file


Use the following to help install the build dependencies

yum install rpmdevtools

Download the source for the specfile
spectool -C rpmbuild/SOURCES/ -g rpmbuild/SPECS/ruby200-p0.spec 

Install the build dependencies
yum-builddep rpmbuild/SPECS/ruby200-p0.spec
